translated: Bäcksin, Johan Viktor Orvar, district judge, Trollhättan, b. 8/7/92 in Gothenburg, son of engineer Victor B. and Agda Arfvidsson. — LL.B. from Uppsala Univ. 16. Clerk in Göta Court of Appeal 16, in Svea Court of Appeal 19, acting auditor there 20, deputy judge 21, judge 22, acting revenue secretary 26, court councilor 30 and 35, revenue judge 32, district judge in Flundre, Väne and Bjärke jurisdiction since 37. Secretary of the 32 bank legislation commission 32-33, chairman of the Älvsburg legal aid association. RNO.
